libcsce.error module¶

Custom error types, primarily related to decoding Beacon config data.

exception libcsce.error.CobaltStrikeError¶

Bases: Exception

Base library error type.

exception libcsce.error.ConfigNotFoundError¶

Bases: libcsce.error.CobaltStrikeError

Raised when a Cobalt Strike config could not be found.

exception libcsce.error.InvalidCSVersionError¶

Bases: libcsce.error.CobaltStrikeError

Raised for unsupported Cobalt Strike versions.

exception libcsce.error.MissingDataSectionError¶

Bases: libcsce.error.CobaltStrikeError

Raised when trying to decrypt a Cobalt Strike config from a PE file without a .data section.

exception libcsce.error.UnsupportedFileTypeError(message)¶

Bases: libcsce.error.CobaltStrikeError

Raised when trying to decrypt a Cobalt Strike config from a non-PE file.
